Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前情提要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Previously on Foundation…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你带了个东西 色彩校正镜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've brought you something. Color-correction 'hesives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你就能看到红绿了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you can see red and green.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他们知道我的与众不同 那会是我在世上的最后一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If they ever learn how different I am, it'll be my last day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射死六只 这一定能让黄昏兄弟印象深刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Six kills. Brother Dusk will be impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这些扔进树丛 我射死了三只\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Throw these in the bushes. I killed three.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法拉想让我们帮她取得战舰的掌控权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Phara wants us to help her take control of the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无敌战舰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Invictus?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个摧毁世界的杀手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A world-killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些老式飞船 需要具备强大处理能力的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These older ships needed something with massive processing power
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来为跃迁提供导航\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to navigate their jumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不得不与飞船直接相连\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They had to be hardwired directly into the ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不做手术可以直接连接吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could someone jack in without the surgery?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那等于判了死刑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It would be a death sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.36,0:01:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（改编自艾萨克阿西莫夫的小说）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.34,0:01:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若问历史学家 “人类最伟大的发明是什么 ”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ask a historian, "What was mankind's greatest invention?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.64,0:01:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火 车轮 刀剑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fire? The wheel? The sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.56,0:01:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会说是历史本身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would argue it's history itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.94,0:01:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,历史不是一种事实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}History isn't fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.23,0:01:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是一种故事 精心策划和塑造的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's narrative, one carefully curated and shaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.53,0:01:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在合适的人笔下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Under the pen strokes of the right scribe,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.07,0:01:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶棍能变成英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a villain becomes a hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谎言能变成真理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a lie becomes the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-爸爸 -怎么了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Daddy? -Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.87,0:01:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们来自哪里  -川陀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Where did we come from? -Trantor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.04,0:02:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 在那之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.63,0:02:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类在哪里诞生 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where did people come from in the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有许多不同的理论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are lots of different theories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.47,0:02:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分认为人类最初 居住在一个单一星球系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Most of them say that humans originally inhabited a single planetary system.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一个 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们甚至不知道是哪一个星球 天狼星 南门二星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we don't even know which. Sirius, Alpha Centauri…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.77,0:02:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人认为我们来自一个叫地球的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some people think that we came from some place called Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.94,0:02:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come here. Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们所知的一切人类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, everyone we know about,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.11,0:02:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都来自同一个地方吗  包括安纳克里昂人和狄斯比斯人 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they also came from the same place? Anacreons and Thespins too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也包括安纳克里昂人和狄斯比斯人 没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anacreons and Thespins too, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他们为什么恨我们 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then how can they hate us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类是复杂的 塞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Being human is complicated, Sal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有共同的起源 也有一些相同的传说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We share a common origin and some of the same myths.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们被大脑所控制\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we're governed by this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.47,0:02:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大脑赋予我们一切理性思考的能力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In here is all the capacity for rational thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:03:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但与此同时 感性情感也存在于大脑中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it's sharing skull space with our emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时感性的声音大过理性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And sometimes emotions shout louder than logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.73,0:03:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些人的感性令他们坚信 帝国对他们不公正\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And somebody's emotions got real insistent that the Empire were doing them wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他们炸毁星桥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So they blew up the Star Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴力是无能者最后的庇护所\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Violence is the last refuge of the incompetent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他们和我们完全不同 对吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, they're not like us at all then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小脑袋里感性的声音也很大呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It gets loud up inside here too, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.76,0:03:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come here. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.85,0:03:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞 问题是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here's the thing, Sal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星桥被炸毁时 数百万人死去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Millions of people died when that Star Bridge came down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后大帝又杀死了数百万的 安纳克里昂人和狄斯比斯人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the Empire killed many millions more on Anacreon and Thespis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以到底谁赢了呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And who won?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:03:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-没有人赢  -没有人赢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Nobody? -Nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那时我们明白了 帝国的灭亡和文明的丧失不可避免\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's how we know that the fall is bound to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过往的行为是预测未来表现的最佳指标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Past behavior is the best predictor of future performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞佛哈定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Salvor Hardin…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在跃迁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're jumping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路易斯 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lewis?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路易斯 你在哪里 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lewis, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,端点星 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Terminus?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们跃迁回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We jumped back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路易斯 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lewis?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:05:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你救了我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心愿护送我们回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You wished us home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,端点星指挥部 我是塞佛哈定 在帝国无敌战舰上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Terminus Control, this is Salvor Hardin, on board the imperial warship Invictus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.02,0:07:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否收到 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.77,0:07:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,端点星指挥部 是否收到 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Terminus Control, do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是塞佛哈定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Salvor Hardin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人能听见吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can anybody hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.47,0:07:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是塞佛哈定 呼叫狄斯比斯骑兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Salvor Hardin calling the Thespin lancers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无敌战舰跃迁了 你们的飞船被带入我们的量子尾波\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Invictus jumped and we've dragged your ships into our quantum wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正在环绕端点星轨道飞行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're in orbit around Terminus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:08:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你能听见 我不知道 如何阻止飞船再次跃迁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you can hear me, I have no idea how to stop this ship from jumping again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许一小时后会跃迁 也许是几天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It could be an hour from now. It could be days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我被困在这里了 除非…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I figure I'm stuck here, unless…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乞丐号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Beggar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么回家 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.57,0:08:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我解释一下详细路线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take me through your route.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个走廊通向哪里 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where does this corridor go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地下灌溉系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The underground irrigation system.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在那上方有一条路可以穿过宫殿废墟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there's a path above it you could take through the old palace ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后你会来到仆从的出口 就在宫殿大门附近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You end up at the servants' exit, right next to the palace gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:09:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以如果我从这里出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, if I could exit here…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超循环站就在那边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hyperloop station's just there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大门安检需要扫描DNA\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gate security has DNA scanners.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要信号消除器 隐藏我的纳米机器人 这样他们就无法追踪我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll need the signal damper. For my nanobots. So they can't track me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我可以给你弄一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think I can get you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想死在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't wanna die in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能保证一切会顺利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't promise it'll all go right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能保证我不会是出错的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All I can promise is I won't be the part that goes wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得走了 黄昏兄弟在…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to go. Brother Dusk is--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克里昂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cleon--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真希望你不叫这个名字 拥有只属于你的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish you had another name. One that was just yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天你可以为我起一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tomorrow you can give me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把信号消除器带给我 我们在另一边见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get me that signal damper, and I'll see you on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 黄昏兄弟 我刚才…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My apologies, Brother Dusk. I was--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.82,0:10:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白 年轻人的时间概念和我不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand. Time flows differently when you're young.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和你说一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to share something with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道 这是我的工作地点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is my workplace, as you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄昏最重要的任务之一 是以画面记录我们的历史\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The signature task of Dusk is to record our visual history.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器人战争的结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The end of the Robot Wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄金马之叛乱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Golden Horse Rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每当我们王朝来到了变革点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Each moment an inflection point for our dynasty,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.43,0:10:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星系的命运似乎都岌岌可危\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when the fate of the galaxy seemed to be hanging in the balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像这一时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As it did here…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我因为蛮族的野蛮之举而惩罚他们的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when I chastened the barbarian worlds for their acts of savagery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:10:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在作画的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And even while I was painting it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:11:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心里想着我们作为历史的谱写者 将如何被描述\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was conscious of how we, as its authors, would be represented.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聪明的艺术家以作品表达论点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A clever artist provides commentary with his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.97,0:11:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是色彩选择这么简单的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even something as simple as a choice of color
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也能传递隐含的意义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}can convey a hidden meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.23,0:11:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时历史性的时刻并不明显\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And sometimes the moment's not so obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时它会被我们忽略\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes it slips past us,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.74,0:11:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直没有意识到它 直到那一刻过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you don't even realize it until it is past,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到你第一次出现在墙上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until your debut on the wall is upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将你画进了我们的画谱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've painted you into our legacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的狩猎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.06,0:11:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到你击中的那三只基力猛龙了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you see the three ghillie raptors you shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.44,0:12:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾梦想有一天 我能做些丰功伟绩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've dreamed of one day doing something,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足以让我有资格出现在这壁画里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}anything, worthy enough to be included in this mural.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道为何这一小事会…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know why this small feat is…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感到很荣幸 谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm honored. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本就知道你具有克里昂一世的伟大品质\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew you had the greatness of Cleon I in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在我们狩猎期间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But during our hunt,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才意识到你还有其他品质\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I realized there was something else inside you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了 你可以独自回顾 属于你的光辉时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll leave you to reflect on your own glorious moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.11,0:12:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用急\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欣赏微妙细腻的笔触吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Appreciate the subtleties.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.15,0:13:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们选择让后代知道什么 对他们隐瞒什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What we choose to tell our children and what we censor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突出什么 简化什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What we illuminate and what we gloss over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,历史是一种不断做加减法的行为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}History as an act of addition and subtraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大帝 请你去元帝塔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Empire, you're needed in the Principium Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我有事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't. I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是黄昏兄弟的要求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brother Dusk insists.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我身体有恙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm indisposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我一分钟 我会去的 只需一分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need a minute alone, and I'll come along. One minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道 我也是大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am also Empire, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.43,0:14:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们都服侍帝国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we both serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘了东西 我需要回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I forgot something. I need to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不急\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封锁入口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lock down the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.10,0:16:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许任何人进出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't let anyone in or out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有条路可以穿过宫殿废墟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a path you can take through the palace ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后你会来到仆从的出口 就在宫殿大门附近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You end up at the servants' exit, right next to the palace gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这条路通向地下灌溉系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This route takes you to the underground irrigation system.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超循环站就在那边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hyperloop station's just there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分散开来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Spread out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警告 水循环即将开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Warning. Water cycling imminent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警告 水循环即将开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Warning. Water cycling imminent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天啊 这个跳跃的距离也太远了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Four moons, that's a long jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乞丐号 快给我醒来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beggar, wake the hell up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎上船 哈定船长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome aboard, Captain Hardin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是帝国护身环 能换你的外套吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's an imperial aura. For your jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能告诉我怎么去33层的德司尼安区吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you tell me how to get to the Desnian Sector on level 33?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.45,0:20:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘坐钴线向下 然后转乘埃利环线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take the Cobalt Line down, then transfer to Ery Loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向核心区走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You wanna head inner core.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.55,0:20:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乞丐号 开启连接端点星的频道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beggar, open a channel to Terminus Control.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通讯频道已开启\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Communications channel open.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,端点星指挥部 我是塞佛哈定 请回答\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Terminus Control, this is Salvor Hardin. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见鬼了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乞丐号 扫描所有波幅 寻找任何可连接的通讯点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beggar, scan all frequencies. Find me anyone on comms.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.57,0:21:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扫描中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Scanning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未发现端点星地表上 存在任何运行的通讯站\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No active comms detected on the surface of Terminus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.96,0:21:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You found someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.12,0:21:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警告 异常碎屑 可能位于撞击轨道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Caution. Anomalous debris on potential intercept trajectory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.59,0:21:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险级别低\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Threat level low.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.13,0:21:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么鬼东西 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.47,0:21:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警告 异常碎屑 确认位于撞击轨道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alert. Anomalous debris on confirmed intercept trajectory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.80,0:21:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险级别中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Threat level moderate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.39,0:21:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要火炮 火炮在哪里 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need guns. Where are the guns?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乞丐号 说明火炮位置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beggar, show me the guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.65,0:21:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警告 异常碎屑即将撞击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Warning. Anomalous debris object impact imminent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.73,0:21:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险级别极高 警告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Threat level severe. Warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.11,0:21:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锁定目标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Target locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.03,0:21:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝贝 是你吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Babe? Babe, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.16,0:21:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨果 是你吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hugo, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.80,0:22:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的计划成功了 塞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our plan worked, Sal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.39,0:22:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么从星带过来的 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How'd you get here from the Belt?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.72,0:22:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主要靠运气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Luck, mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.10,0:22:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我联络上狄斯比斯指挥部 我搭上了其中一艘骑兵飞船的副驾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I made contact with Thespin Command. I rode shotgun on one of the lancers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.94,0:22:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发现无敌战舰即将跃迁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then I could see the Invictus was about to jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.27,0:22:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我拿了一个麻醉棍 让自己晕了过去 以进行跃迁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I grabbed a sedation stick and knocked myself out for the jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.61,0:22:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提醒其他人也这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Warned the rest of my people to do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.41,0:22:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒来就听见你美妙的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I woke up to the dulcet tones of your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.95,0:22:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不明白为什么你这么快醒来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I don't understand how you woke up so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.37,0:22:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并没有真的睡过去 就和穹窿一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never went to sleep. It's like the Vault.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.04,0:22:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法解释原因 但跃迁对我没有影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't explain how or why, but the jump just didn't affect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.09,0:22:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你带我们回到端点星了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you got us back to Terminus?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.92,0:22:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那是路易斯的功劳 他为了送我们回家牺牲了自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, that was Lewis. He died to get us back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基地没有回应 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the Foundation's not responding?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.80,0:23:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有任何人回应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one is,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.68,0:23:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连法拉留下的安纳克里昂人都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not even the Anacreons Phara left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.98,0:23:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是空域的作用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the null field.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.65,0:23:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能感觉到 雨果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can feel it, Hugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.28,0:23:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它变得更大 更响了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's… even bigger. It's… louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.45,0:23:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像在慢慢包裹整个星球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's like it's enveloped the whole planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.29,0:23:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须阻止它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.12,0:23:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你疯了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.00,0:23:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是他们都死了呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if they're all dead down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.00,0:23:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如我们直接离开 就现在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if we just left? Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.88,0:23:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以去红廊避难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll make a run for the Red Corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.30,0:23:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以带你看艾琳娜四号星 长庚星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll show you Irina Four, I'll show you Hesperus--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.22,0:23:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能这么做 雨果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't, Hugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.64,0:23:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这场危机并没有解决方案呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if there is no solution to this crisis?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.22,0:23:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果谢顿的预测是错的呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if Seldon got it wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.40,0:24:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须坚持到最后 雨果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to see this through, Hugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.20,0:24:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须挽回局面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.00,0:24:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你希望我怎么做 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.84,0:24:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无敌战舰会再次跃迁 除非你的人能够关闭它的驱动器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Invictus is gonna jump again unless your people can disable its drives.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.22,0:24:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就让它跃迁 让它带走法拉 我们再也不用见它了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then let it jump. Let it take Phara. It'll be out of our lives forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.76,0:24:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.26,0:24:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基地需要这艘飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Foundation needs that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.52,0:24:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我们终结危机的办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the way we end the crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.69,0:24:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我无法告诉你如何… -我只是有种感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I can't tell you how… -I just have a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.61,0:24:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说过你对我坚信不疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said you have absolute faith in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.50,0:24:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的信念动摇了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You still believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.96,0:24:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果现在改变主意 我是不是有点过分 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be kind of a dick if I changed my mind now, wouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.98,0:25:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在目的地见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll see you on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.16,0:25:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.45,0:25:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.52,0:25:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你人生的每一分 每一秒 都在别人的注视下度过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've lived every moment of your life with people watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.85,0:25:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疤痕区不是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Scar's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.48,0:26:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以在那里混入人群\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can lose yourself in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.90,0:26:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于帝国而言 疤痕区代表着失败\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For Empire, the Scar represents a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.86,0:26:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于川陀的其他人来说 它是一次机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the rest of Trantor, it represents an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.24,0:26:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数百年来的第一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the first time in centuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.91,0:26:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以抬头看见真的云朵和星辰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we can look up and see real clouds, real stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.33,0:26:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是为了让我们安于现状的 服务器运行模拟天空\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not a simulation run by servers designed to keep us complacent.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.18,0:26:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我居住在第33层的德司尼安区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I live on level 33, in the Desnian Sector.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.61,0:26:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老特尔夏做的风味马尔卡饼 是整个星球最美味的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Old Tertia makes the best spiced malkas on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.36,0:26:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我称之为家的走廊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the corridor I take home.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.95,0:26:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你的宫殿是两个天地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's nothing like your palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.41,0:26:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里吵闹喧嚣 熙熙攘攘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's chaotic. It's crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.97,0:27:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这里是鲜活的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.18,0:27:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它正等着你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it's waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.37,0:27:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能再等了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I couldn't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.94,0:28:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有戴护身环\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not wearing your aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.19,0:28:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用它换了这件外套 以免别人认出我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I traded it for this, so I wouldn't be recognized.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.24,0:28:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换外套这招挺聪明的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The jacket's smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.41,0:28:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们可以烧了它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now we can burn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.01,0:28:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得移除我的纳米机器人 以防他们在追踪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to get my nanobots removed in case they're tracking me. I…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.85,0:28:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也许根本不该留在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I probably shouldn't even stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.60,0:28:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 我有信号消除器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's okay. I got the signal damper.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.69,0:28:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它可以隐藏你的踪迹 直到我们…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That'll cover you until we can arrange to…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.32,0:28:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.70,0:28:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最难的部分已经结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The hardest part's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.12,0:29:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你逃离了他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got away from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.92,0:29:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来到这里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.05,0:29:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 说真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, truthfully…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.01,0:29:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身上的味道仍然很难闻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you still smell terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.56,0:29:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如你洗个澡吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why don't you shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.09,0:29:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 我在想给自己起个新名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, I was thinking about a new name for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.26,0:30:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿祖拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Azura?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.94,0:30:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是用来做什么的 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.01,0:31:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞佛说引擎室在那边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}According to Salvor, the engine room is that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.56,0:31:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有大约33个小时来关闭跃迁驱动器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've got about thirty-three hours to disable the jumpdrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.69,0:31:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里发生了什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.19,0:31:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个漫长而可怕的故事 没有人活下来讲述它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A long and terrible story that no one's alive to tell…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.65,0:31:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安纳克里昂人在哪 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anacreons, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.66,0:31:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰桥那边 塞佛把他们绑在那里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The bridge. Salvor has them tied up in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.58,0:31:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.18,0:32:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一位智者曾说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A wise man once said,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.10,0:32:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“没有历史的民族就如无根的树”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"A people without history is like a tree without roots."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.06,0:32:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位智者的历史缺失了什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's missing from the wise man's history?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.73,0:32:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从何时开始 故事代替了事实 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When did story replace record?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.24,0:32:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当所有事实都不再可信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When all the facts fall short of believability,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.87,0:32:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻想反而有一种令人安心的真实感\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}fantasy feels reassuringly solid.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.91,0:32:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而由于这是我的历史\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And since this is my history,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.71,0:32:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以决定删减哪一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I get to decide which parts have been subtracted,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.67,0:32:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,增添哪一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which have been added.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.13,0:34:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jord?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.91,0:35:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mom? Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.41,0:35:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…醒醒 是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mom. Mom, wake up, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.58,0:35:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…醒醒 是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mom. Mom, wake up, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.81,0:35:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能理解它吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you make anything of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.05,0:36:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我自己破解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fine. I'll figure it out myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.83,0:36:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松开拳头 塞佛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Open your fists, Salvor.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.96,0:36:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松开拳头 塞佛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Open your fists, Salvor.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.46,0:36:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.73,0:37:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能理解它吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you make anything of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.56,0:37:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞佛 如果你是计划的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Salvor, if you were part of the Plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.27,0:37:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我会更容易相信这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it would make it a lot easier for me to believe in all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.04,0:37:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你用了多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long did it take you…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.88,0:37:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,激活元光体 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to trigger the Prime Radiant?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.00,0:37:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第二次尝试时成功了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got it on the second try.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.52,0:37:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,历史是终极武器 因为它能驾驭时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}History is the ultimate weapon, because it harnesses time itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.90,0:37:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正确地利用时间 过去就能改变现在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Used correctly, the past can alter the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.28,0:37:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有哪种发明能够做到这点 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What other invention can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.00,0:38:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞佛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Salvor?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.38,0:38:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.93,0:39:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我还以为再也见不到你了 -我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I thought I'd never see you again. -Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.40,0:39:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空域停止了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The null field, it's stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.12,0:39:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你做的吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.97,0:39:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是门吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that a door?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.14,0:39:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.68,0:39:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那现在怎么办 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.64,0:39:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是结束的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now is where it ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.86,0:40:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到猎手了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you find the Huntress?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.95,0:40:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们搜寻了整艘飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We searched the entire ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.66,0:40:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有她的踪迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No sign of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.91,0:40:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Except this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.25,0:40:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们尽快赶到端点星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then we get down to Terminus as fast as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.75,0:40:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑曜岩号 开启与长石砂岩号 和片麻岩号的通讯频道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Obsidian, open a channel to Arkose and Gneiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.67,0:40:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通讯频道已开启\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Communications channel open.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.93,0:40:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是狄斯比斯指挥部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Thespin Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.55,0:40:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有骑兵立即前往星球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want all lancers planet-side immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.72,0:40:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞船由你们中的谁指挥 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which one of you is this ship slave to?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.19,0:40:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让飞船听命于法拉柯恩 否则你也会死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Slave this ship to Phara Keaen, or you die too.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.15,0:40:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长石砂岩号 启动规程 飞船转移 法拉柯恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Arkose, invoke protocol. Ship transfer, Phara Keaen.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.21,0:40:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心率增加\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Heart rate's rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.26,0:41:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果达到120次 那么机器人会进入紧急模式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If it gets to 120, then the bots go into crisis mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.47,0:41:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会增加抑制剂量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll increase the inhibitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.23,0:41:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脉搏渐渐平稳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pulse is stabilizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.27,0:41:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始传输吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Start the transfer now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.10,0:41:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正将你的纳米机器人传输至我的血液\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're transferring your nanobots into my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.57,0:42:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你想要的 对吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what you wanted, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.69,0:42:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移除它们 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To have them removed?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.28,0:42:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.49,0:42:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黎明的克隆人 显而易见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A Dawn clone, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.62,0:42:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在外表上与你一模一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Superficially identical to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.54,0:42:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你是如何…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But how are you…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.41,0:42:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来到这里 而不是漂浮在水族箱里 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here? Instead of floating in an aquarium?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.09,0:42:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的人成功将克里昂一世的部分DNA 从宫殿中偷出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our people managed to smuggle some of Cleon I's DNA out of the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.42,0:42:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了这一天 我们已经努力了数十年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've been working towards this day for decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.43,0:42:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你出乎我们的意料 我们原计划明天才帮你逃出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You surprised us. We'd planned to have you escape tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.06,0:42:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿祖拉在哪里 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's Azura?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.24,0:42:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切都是陷阱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This was all a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.45,0:42:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么能这样对我 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How could you do this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.20,0:42:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.33,0:42:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这关乎星系的其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is about the rest of the galaxy,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.54,0:42:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有被帝国压迫的星球和人民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}all the planets and people who've been crushed under the Empire's heel.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.75,0:42:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是他的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.33,0:43:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是在这种环境下长大的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's how he was raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.30,0:43:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来 他和他的兄弟们总是听人们说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He and his brothers have always been told
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.63,0:43:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是不会灭的明光 永不断裂的锁链\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they are the light that never dims, an unbroken chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.60,0:43:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们那小天地的宫墙隔离了残酷的现实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Reality just doesn't penetrate their little terrarium.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.60,0:43:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你要如何忍受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know how you're gonna stomach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.85,0:43:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会有事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.85,0:43:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经练习扮演这个角色太久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been practicing my role long enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.94,0:43:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚在成长的小暴君\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the cloistered little tyrant in the making…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.65,0:43:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身上笼罩着一种微弱的 自怜又自负的高冷气质\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}projecting that subtle air of self-pitying, arrogant indifference.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.83,0:43:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,练习 你在说什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Practicing? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.38,0:43:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“练习 你在说什么 ”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Practicing? What are you talking about?"
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.96,0:43:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是你的替身 黎明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm your understudy, Dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.88,0:43:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我该登上舞台了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now it's time for me to take center stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.97,0:43:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会回到宫殿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going to go back to the palace,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.26,0:43:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I'm gonna be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.27,0:43:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会杀了你 他们知道我不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll just kill you then. They know I'm different.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.27,0:44:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 可是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.52,0:44:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我与你不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.40,0:44:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并非色盲 我不是左撇子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not color-blind. I'm not left-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.78,0:44:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在基因上 我与克里昂一世一模一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm genetically identical to Cleon I.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.08,0:44:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以证明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I can prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.54,0:44:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.54,0:44:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能你与一世一模一样而我却不是 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How can you be identical to the first, and I'm not?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.63,0:44:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,技术术语是“磁性纳米粒子转染”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Magnetic nanoparticle transfection" is the technical term.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.59,0:44:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具体情况太过复杂 我也不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all a little over my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.51,0:44:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是简单说来 在克隆你之后 他们修改了你的DNA\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but, basically, they altered your DNA after the fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.26,0:44:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如我说的 在你我出生之前 这一切都已计划好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like I said, this has been planned since before you or I took our first breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.85,0:44:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的人明白必须让你离开宫殿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our people knew they had to get you out of the palace,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.64,0:44:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他们不能直接绑走你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but they couldn't just take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.94,0:44:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样太危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That would've been too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.06,0:44:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们必须让你自己选择离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They had to make it so you'd choose to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.23,0:44:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要一个逃走的动机 还有比生存更好的动机吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You needed a motive to run. And what better motive than survival?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.20,0:44:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大帝 是我们让你变得不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're the ones who made you different, Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.16,0:45:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从某种意义而言 你其实很幸运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a certain way, you're lucky too.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.33,0:45:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一脉相承的王朝是人类的耻辱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Genetic Dynasty's an affront to humanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.67,0:45:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你已不是其中的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you're no longer part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.76,0:45:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从来都不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You never really were.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.68,0:45:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传输完成了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The transfer's complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.62,0:45:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从头到尾 你没有任何选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You had no choice in any of this…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.17,0:45:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们仍然感谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but thank you just the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.80,0:45:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扶他起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.89,0:46:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要对我做什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you gonna do to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.64,0:46:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得呢 克里昂 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you think, Cleon?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.30,0:46:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿祖拉…这边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Azura. Azura, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.07,0:46:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.45,0:46:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄昏兄弟 我真感激\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brother Dusk! I am so grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.74,0:47:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彻底审查所有死者的记忆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want a full memory audit of all the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.20,0:47:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这女孩呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.46,0:47:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这女孩 是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The girl. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.26,0:47:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演技令人赞叹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quite a performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.01,0:47:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为观众欣赏这场表演 很荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was a pleasure to observe it,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.05,0:47:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只能蒙骗年轻人和傻子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}tailored though it was to the young and foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.69,0:47:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会认为 我们会任由这个无人机离开宫殿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't really think we'd let this drone leave the palace
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.99,0:47:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不通知我们吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}without alerting us, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.99,0:47:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的 我们一路跟随你们 令人激动的旅程 回到这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We followed your whole enticing travelogue home, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.17,0:47:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你放他走 从而跟着他找到我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You let him get away so he would lead you to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.13,0:47:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捆缚她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shroud her.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.19,0:48:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经得到你想要的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got what you wanted then.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.03,0:48:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远别以为你理解我想要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never presume to understand what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.41,0:48:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你愚蠢 天真 易受骗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are stupid, naive, gullible.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.00,0:48:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在你这个年纪也是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So was I at your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.92,0:48:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是可以原谅的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And these things are forgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.67,0:48:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你的不同之处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the matter of your… difference,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.13,0:48:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个问题则复杂得多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that's rather more complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.68,0:48:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你一定也听到他们的话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you must've heard them.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.68,0:48:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是受害者 我们都是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm a victim. We all are.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.43,0:48:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.89,0:48:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这让你变成我们脆弱的象征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that makes you the embodiment of our vulnerability,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.36,0:48:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个令人不快的标识 提醒着我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}an ugly reminder of the knife-edge
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.07,0:49:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一脉相承的王朝之根基如此脆弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}upon which our Genetic Dynasty is balanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.36,0:49:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有何理由会想再看到你的脸 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By what logic would we want to look on your face ever again?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.20,0:49:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的脸 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My face?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.08,0:49:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的脸就是你的脸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My face is your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.67,0:49:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管逻辑 试着换位思考一下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forget logic. Try empathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.47,0:49:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.35,0:49:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不是你说了算 而取决于白昼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Surely it's not up to you. It's up to Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.85,0:49:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}True.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.48,0:49:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白昼兄弟很快将回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brother Day will be home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.90,0:49:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以向他求情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can plead your case to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.69,0:49:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜他在经历了少女星的事之后 应该是心烦意乱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I doubt his experience on the Maiden has made him serene.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.04,0:49:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守卫者 你安全返回了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Warden, you made it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.54,0:49:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两人离我远点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep your distance, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.21,0:50:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但大家都醒了 已经结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But everyone's waking up. It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.47,0:50:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not over.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.05,0:50:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞佛 等等 别过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Salvor, wait. Don't go in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.64,0:50:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须这么做 妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.76,0:50:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别去 止步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You will not! Step away.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.18,0:50:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说过这不是陷阱 你不知道这是什么情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said this wasn't a trick, that you didn't know what this was.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.48,0:50:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们确实不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.56,0:50:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你的女儿却让它停止了 你要如何解释 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And yet your daughter has tamed it. How do you explain that?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.34,0:51:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 塞 我试图说服他们别着陆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry, Sal. I tried to talk 'em out of landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.13,0:51:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这是合理的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, this makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.05,0:51:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该在这里 所有事件汇合为一场危机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is where I'm supposed to be. Everything converging in a single crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.56,0:51:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的猎手在哪 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is our Huntress?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.73,0:51:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她失去了对无敌战舰的控制\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She lost control of the Invictus.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.40,0:51:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们殉道 摧毁川陀的计划已经失败了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your plans for martyrdom, for Trantor, they're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.23,0:51:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗文 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rowan?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.32,0:51:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维伊尔德诸神已经背弃我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Weald Gods have forsaken us.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.35,0:52:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 真该死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, hammered shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.53,0:52:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这画面真美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, isn't this a pretty picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.96,0:52:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新旧敌人齐聚一堂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enemies old and new, conveniently gathered in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.38,0:52:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下武器 给他松绑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Drop your weapons and unbind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.10,0:53:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 守卫者 别想着抛你那枚硬币\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you, Warden, don't even think about flashing that coin of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.44,0:53:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法拉 很高兴你还活着 真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm glad you're alive, Phara, truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.78,0:53:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你也听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you to hear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.86,0:53:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最不想听的就是你的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Last thing I'm interested in hearing is more words from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.36,0:53:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法拉 拜托了 跃迁会导致精神错乱 你的思维不理性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Phara, please. The jump induces psychosis. You're not thinking straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.91,0:53:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的思维没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm thinking just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.21,0:53:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄准目标的能力也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Also aiming.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.46,0:53:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 如果你不喜欢我接下来的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, if you don't like what I have to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.67,0:53:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说完话 你可以杀了我 你可以杀死所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you can kill me when I'm done. You can kill all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.51,0:53:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.01,0:53:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那艘飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That ship…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.27,0:53:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们族群将取得的最强大武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is the most powerful weapon your people will ever get their hands on.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.48,0:53:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是这样 为何摧毁它 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If that's the case, why destroy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.82,0:53:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-为何不利用它  -如何利用 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Why not use it for leverage? -How?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.49,0:53:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们团结起来 三个世界的人齐心协力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We band together, all three worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.74,0:53:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再移动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.04,0:54:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以共享无敌战舰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can share the Invictus.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.87,0:54:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以合作修好它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can repair it, together.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.00,0:54:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只需要让理性的声音比感性更响亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All we have to do is let our logic speak louder than our emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.68,0:54:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法拉 停下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Phara, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.10,0:54:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要与你们的猎手为敌 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You would take up arms against your own Huntress?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.98,0:54:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狩猎行动结束了 法拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The hunt is over, Phara.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.54,0:54:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法拉 停下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Phara, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.94,0:55:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-瞄准 -弗里斯通 等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Take aim! -Freestone, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.83,0:55:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她死了 放下武器吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's gone. Drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.47,0:55:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼前的景象令人鼓舞啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, this is encouraging.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.56,0:55:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安纳克里昂人 狄斯比斯人和端点星人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anacreons, Thespins, and Termini.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.02,0:55:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见到大家齐聚在此 我看到了希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seeing you all gathered here gives me hope…
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.94,0:55:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我们真的能取得成功\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we might actually pull this off.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.96,0:56:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,字幕翻译：易晗
